1
00:00:20,200 --> 00:00:21,600
Come on. Let me carry you.

2
00:00:22,080 --> 00:00:22,840
No.

3
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:24,400
You can't press on my stomach.

4
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:25,160
Cover it.

5
00:00:25,160 --> 00:00:25,840
I'll help you down.

6
00:00:25,840 --> 00:00:26,200
Okay.

7
00:00:26,440 --> 00:00:27,120
Thank you.

8
00:00:27,760 --> 00:00:28,440
Slow down.

9
00:00:32,920 --> 00:00:33,720
Slow down.

10
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:35,360
Watch out.

11
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:40,120
Be careful.

12
00:00:40,120 --> 00:00:40,960
Help me!

13
00:00:41,840 --> 00:00:42,840
Help me!

14
00:00:43,640 --> 00:00:44,520
Can you still walk?

15
00:00:44,520 --> 00:00:45,600
I... I can't walk.

16
00:00:47,040 --> 00:00:47,720
I'm coming up right now.

17
00:00:47,720 --> 00:00:48,520
Hang in there.

18
00:00:49,080 --> 00:00:49,640
Let's go.

19
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:51,520
Slow down.

20
00:00:54,440 --> 00:00:55,240
Be careful.

21
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:02,240
Hang in there.

22
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:02,840
They're here.

23
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:03,900
Don't fall asleep.

24
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:05,120
Where's the ambulance?

25
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:06,600
It's still two blocks away.

26
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:07,840
Let's get her to the neighborhood entrance first

27
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:08,640
to save time.

28
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:10,520
Careful. Hold her.

29
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:16,730
Give me the clothes.

30
00:01:16,960 --> 00:01:18,690
Get her to the hospital, quick.

31
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,039
Are you okay?

32
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,120
I'll help you down.

33
00:02:13,760 --> 00:02:15,820
Wang Luyang, Ning Yuxin, and Liu Rong

34
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,320
all used to live in Building 7.

35
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:19,200
But none of them mentioned it.

36
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:20,360
Ning Yuxin and her dad

37
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,560
lived in 603,

38
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,480
while Wang Luyang

39
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:25,000
and his ex-girlfriend He Huan lived in 1001.

40
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:27,200
There was a fire in Building 7 last year.

41
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:28,960
It killed He Huan, who was pregnant,

42
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:31,820
and left Ning Yuxin's father in a vegetative state.

43
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,120
After the fire,

44
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,960
they both moved out of Building 7.

45
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,960
But recently,

46
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:38,520
they returned as a couple.

47
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,040
And Liu Rong

48
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,160
rented apartment 1801.

49
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:42,400
Cheng Jiancai died in that very apartment.

50
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,800
Liu Rong was at the scene.

51
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:46,000
A savior turned accomplice.

52
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:47,000
Does that make sense?

53
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:49,320
There's something weird about Wang Luyang.

54
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:50,050
Look at this.

55
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:53,600
He Huan and Wang Luyang had a great relationship.

56
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:55,040
After she got pregnant last year,

57
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:56,520
they were planning to get married.

58
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:58,760
But she died before they could.

59
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:01,760
How could Wang Luyang, in just one year,

60
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,760
fall in love with Ning Yuxin,

61
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,200
and even live with her

62
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:06,930
where his ex-girlfriend died?

63
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:07,840
If you ask me,

64
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:10,000
Wang Luyang and Ning Yuxin

65
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,600
aren't a real couple.

66
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:13,160
They're out for revenge.

67
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:15,930
They chose this building for the murders.

68
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:18,040
It seems like they're avenging that fire.

69
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:20,640
But what does Cheng Jiancai have to do with the fire?

70
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,500
Captain Zheng,

71
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,560
I found the cause of the fire.

72
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:26,079
It started with a short circuit.

73
00:03:26,079 --> 00:03:27,480
But the insulation boards lacked fire retardant,

74
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:30,240
which is the main reason the fire got out of control.

75
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:32,040
Cheng Jiancai cut corners on the insulation boards,

76
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:33,840
and then completely washed his hands of it.

77
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:35,570
There were no fire retardants.

78
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:36,760
To save costs,

79
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:37,880
he treated human lives as a joke.

80
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:39,480
The authorities investigated for a year,

81
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:42,000
and finally found out Cheng Jiancai is the real culprit.

82
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:44,260
But Cheng Jiancai is Liu Rong's husband.

83
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:47,280
kill her husband together?

84
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,880
Could the death of Liu Rong's ex-husband

85
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:50,760
be related to that fire?

86
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,250
That's impossible.

87
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,040
Liu Rong's ex-husband, Yin Haohan,

88
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:56,700
went missing before the fire.

89
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:57,400
Besides,

90
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:59,530
Cheng Jiancai didn't know Yin Haohan.

91
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:00,520
The fire.

92
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:02,640
Yin Haohan.

93
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:04,760
How did you and Yin Haohan

94
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:05,720
know each other?

95
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:08,480
We met a few times,

96
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:10,120
but we weren't close.

97
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:12,780
Chen Yishi.

98
00:04:13,040 --> 00:04:15,040
Go check if Yin Haohan and Cheng Jiancai

99
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:16,720
ever worked on any projects together.

100
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,180
Jin Jin.

101
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,800
Go ask Cheng Caiyun.

102
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,120
Check if Cheng Jiancai

103
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,920
has ever worked in cold storage.

104
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:22,800
Okay.

105
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,360
Let's begin.

106
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:00,120
Ning Yuxin.

107
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,520
As for the fire,

108
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,800
we've already investigated it.

109
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:06,700
I know why your father is in the hospital.

110
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:07,920
I also know

111
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:10,690
why you need money so badly.

112
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,180
Of the three of you,

113
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,480
only one can go home.

114
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,360
I hope it's you.

115
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,060
I hope even more

116
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,720
that when your father opens his eyes,

117
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,050
the first person he sees

118
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:30,880
is you.

119
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:33,240
I know you're indebted to Liu Rong.

120
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,500
I also know that you two

121
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,400
have reached some kind of agreement.

122
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:38,460
But you have to look out for yourself.

123
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:39,840
You aren't allies.

124
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,720
You're accomplices.

125
00:05:42,320 --> 00:05:42,960
Allies

126
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:44,680
share the profits.

127
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:46,330
But accomplices

128
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,409
share the sentence.

129
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,080
Sometimes, crime

130
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:56,300
is just a split-second decision.

131
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:58,740
I hope you think this through.

132
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:00,680
Ning Yuxin.

133
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,460
If you're not the mastermind,

134
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,320
I advise you

135
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:06,920
to tell us exactly what happened.

136
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,440
If they talk before you do,

137
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:11,800
you won't have the upper hand.

138
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,320
The one who gets to go home early

139
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:16,520
might not be you.

140
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:20,520
Ning Yuxin.

141
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:24,720
Your dad worked hard to raise you alone.

142
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:27,120
You finally graduated,

143
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,000
and he can rely on you now.

144
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:31,440
Do you want to stay here forever?

145
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:40,500
I don't want to disappoint my dad.

146
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,560
Thank you for tying my hair.

147
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:47,480
Growing up, no one else tied my hair.

148
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,650
It was always my dad.

149
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,480
I'll talk.

150
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:59,200
I didn't mean to kill him.

151
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:01,440
I just wanted to scheme with Wang Luyang

152
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:03,440
to get some money.

153
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,480
I know they hate him,

154
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:09,000
but they aren't bad people.

155
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:11,880
The only bad one is Cheng Jiancai.

156
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:13,720
Why did you move out last year

157
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:15,410
only to move back this year?

158
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,520
That place...

159
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:18,280
few people dare to live there now.

160
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:19,800
The rent is cheap.

161
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,240
Cheap?

162
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:24,410
If it's cheap, why only rent it for a month?

163
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:26,240
Look at me.

164
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,720
Do I look like I have any money?

165
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,920
Anyway, I figured

166
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,480
I'd rent a place to scam some money.

167
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,840
What if you succeeded?

168
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,480
Then I'd keep renting.

169
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,600
Why did you scam money?

170
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,480
My girlfriend's father

171
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,480
is in a vegetative state.

172
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:38,120
Medical treatment costs money.

173
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,520
All for your girlfriend?

174
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:40,480
You're love-struck?

175
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,210
No, Officer.

176
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,320
How can you say that?

177
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,780
She's going to spend her life with me.

178
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:47,159
As a man,

179
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:48,600
I have to take full responsibility.

180
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,920
Take full responsibility?

181
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,120
If you were really responsible,

182
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:53,050
would she be handcuffed next door?

183
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:55,400
Wang Luyang.

184
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,659
Let me ask you something else.

185
00:07:57,880 --> 00:07:59,880
When did you start dating Ning Yuxin?

186
00:07:59,880 --> 00:08:01,240
Just around the New Year.

187
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:01,920
Then,

188
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:04,180
what about your ex-girlfriend, He Huan?

189
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,520
How long did you date?

190
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,120
Ten years.

191
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,040
Ten years.

192
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,560
My wife and I have been married for exactly ten years.

193
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,840
Our child is still young.

194
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:20,240
If my wife were pregnant,

195
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:22,300
and died in a fire along with the baby,

196
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,720
I would hate everyone,

197
00:08:25,280 --> 00:08:26,340
including myself.

198
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:28,080
Do you hate yourself?

199
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,200
I do.

200
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:37,320
Back then, my wife and I,

201
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,480
to have this child,

202
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,679
put in a lot of effort.

203
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:41,679
I know how hard it was for my wife.

204
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,200
He Huan got pregnant out of wedlock.

205
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:47,320
Do you know anything about that?

206
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:51,240
Take a look.

207
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:53,840
Over five months.

208
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,200
It was fully formed.

209
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,360
A woman,

210
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:01,520
having a child before marriage.

211
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:02,800
Such a big fire.

212
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:04,640
Over two hundred steps.

213
00:09:04,920 --> 00:09:06,920
If she ran too fast, she'd hurt the baby.

214
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:08,580
If she ran too slow, she'd die.

215
00:09:08,640 --> 00:09:10,440
She's only been gone for just over a year,

216
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:13,320
and you moved back in with another woman just to save money?

217
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,640
Are you actually glad

218
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:16,900
that your ex-wife brought the rent down?

219
00:09:16,920 --> 00:09:18,520
Are you even human?

220
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:21,880
I'm not human.

221
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:23,880
I'm not a human being.

222
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:45,680
Listen.

223
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,400
Listen.

224
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:52,000
I called everyone here.

225
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:54,530
Cheng Jiancai is the murderer.

226
00:09:54,680 --> 00:09:55,810
He killed Yin Haohan

227
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,320
and caused that fire.

228
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,040
Ms. Liu,

229
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,320
look at this.

230
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:12,320
Why do you have this phone?

231
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,320
I bought it.

232
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:14,160
I charged it,

233
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:15,220
saw the wallpaper,

234
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:17,810
and realized it must be your husband's phone.

235
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:20,080
Ms. Liu,

236
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,440
There is something

237
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:23,500
that I don't know if I should mention.

238
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:25,840
Go ahead.

239
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:28,450
I think I found your husband's killer.

240
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:31,000
The last text Haohan wrote before he died

241
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:31,800
was for you,

242
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,280
but he never sent it.

243
00:10:33,680 --> 00:10:35,120
There's a problem with the insulation material.

244
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:35,920
Yes.

245
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:38,340
Cheng Jiancai killed him.

246
00:10:42,520 --> 00:10:43,640
Carbon dioxide.

247
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:45,240
Low temperature.

248
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,680
Enclosed space.

249
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:47,680
Movement.

250
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,000
Dai Yu,

251
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,920
Wang Luyang and Ning Yuxin confessed.

252
00:10:54,920 --> 00:10:57,120
They got together because of that fire.

253
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,360
Then why did Liu Rong

254
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,490
kill Cheng Jiancai?

255
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:00,840
Yin Haohan's death

256
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,120
was related to Cheng Jiancai.

257
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,600
When Wang Luyang was fixing phones,

258
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:05,200
he accidentally got Yin Haohan's phone.

259
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:07,880
Cheng Jiancai used to work at the cold storage on Wenjing Road.

260
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:08,600
Back then,

261
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:10,600
he was in charge of transporting raw meat.

262
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,860
I know where the primary crime scene was.

263
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,400
It was inside the refrigerated truck.

264
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:15,400
Inside the truck,

265
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:17,680
the dry ice used to keep the meat fresh

266
00:11:17,680 --> 00:11:19,720
sublimated into a large amount of carbon dioxide.

267
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:21,640
That's why his body showed signs of poisoning

268
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:22,500
and frostbite.

269
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,200
Also,

270
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:25,240
the hanging meat inside the truck,

271
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,640
as the vehicle moved,

272
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:27,640
kept hitting him.

273
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:28,880
This explains

274
00:11:29,040 --> 00:11:30,120
why those abrasions

275
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:31,320
appeared on his body.

276
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:33,120
Because it was a refrigerated truck.

277
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:34,880
So it's not strange that he was put in the cold storage.

278
00:11:34,880 --> 00:11:36,480
After his body was frozen,

279
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:39,040
it was quickly moved to the cold storage.

280
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:41,280
So his body preserved

281
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:43,650
ice crystals from both environments.

282
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:46,540
So the frostbite on Cheng Jiancai's hand

283
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:49,200
was caused when he dumped the body in the cold storage.

284
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:51,920
As for why Cheng Jiancai lost control in 1801,

285
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:53,880
it was because he was drugged with an aphrodisiac.

286
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:55,920
During his struggle with Wang Luyang,

287
00:11:55,920 --> 00:11:56,920
due to the drug's effect,

288
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:57,840
his heart raced,

289
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:58,920
and he had trouble moving.

290
00:11:58,920 --> 00:12:00,120
That gave Wang Luyang

291
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,570
the chance to tie him up.

292
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,400
He was struck many times.

293
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:05,080
The final blow from the massager

294
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:06,280
was the direct cause of death.

295
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:08,400
If he was struck repeatedly,

296
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:11,460
the fingerprints on the massager shouldn't be so neat.

297
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:14,120
Maybe the fingerprints on the massager

298
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:15,280
were wiped off

299
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:16,680
and then pressed back on.

300
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:20,200
Alright, Captain Zheng.

301
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,280
Making the dead speak,

302
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:22,560
I've done my part.

303
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,000
Now,

304
00:12:26,560 --> 00:12:28,690
it's your turn to make the living talk.

305
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:33,690
I want to report a crime.

306
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:36,440
Yin Haohan

307
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,760
was killed by my brother.

308
00:12:55,520 --> 00:12:57,120
Then why are you reporting it now?

309
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,400
My brother is dead.

310
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:00,600
I have nothing left to hide.

311
00:13:01,920 --> 00:13:03,160
Liu Rong must know

312
00:13:03,160 --> 00:13:04,680
that my brother killed Yin Haohan.

313
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:05,800
So I am convinced

314
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:08,320
that my brother was killed by Liu Rong.

315
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:11,720
Liu Rong held a grudge because my brother killed her husband.

316
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:13,080
That bitch, Liu Rong.

317
00:13:13,560 --> 00:13:15,960
From the moment she got close to my brother,

318
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:18,360
she was preparing to take revenge on him.

319
00:13:18,920 --> 00:13:19,960
What evidence do you have?

320
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:21,560
I am the evidence.

321
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,600
If you want evidence,

322
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:24,200
you can investigate it yourselves.

323
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,760
I'm telling you all this

324
00:13:25,760 --> 00:13:28,040
just to bring Liu Rong to justice.

325
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:31,200
I want her to rot in prison for the rest of her life.

326
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:32,680
Cheng Caiyun.

327
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:33,800
Stop right there.

328
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,880
You are suspected of concealing criminal facts.

329
00:13:35,880 --> 00:13:38,560
You are now being summoned in accordance with the law.

330
00:13:38,560 --> 00:13:39,960
The truth about Yin Haohan's death,

331
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:41,360
we have already told you.

332
00:13:41,920 --> 00:13:43,320
As for Cheng Jiancai's death,

333
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:45,450
I hope you can give us the truth as well.

334
00:13:45,560 --> 00:13:47,160
I was the one who called them.

335
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:49,400
They need money.

336
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:51,200
So I suggested setting a trap

337
00:13:51,400 --> 00:13:52,800
to let Cheng Jiancai take the money,

338
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:53,440
and I

339
00:13:54,280 --> 00:13:56,680
could use this chance to find out the truth.

340
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:58,200
But I didn't expect

341
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:01,890
that Cheng Jiancai didn't actually want to marry me.

342
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:04,000
He just wanted to get revenge on me.

343
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:04,760
Liar.

344
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,720
And you claim you aren't partners.

345
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:10,720
I didn't even give you Liu Rong's number,

346
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:12,080
yet you brought her here.

347
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:12,560
You are just

348
00:14:12,560 --> 00:14:13,760
teaming up to scam me.

349
00:14:13,880 --> 00:14:14,960
Bullshit.

350
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:16,560
You want money, don't you?

351
00:14:16,560 --> 00:14:17,320
I don't have any.

352
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,400
She has an apartment

353
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:19,730
right in this building.

354
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:20,920
Go ask her for it.

355
00:14:20,920 --> 00:14:23,120
That is the home I shared with Yin Haohan.

356
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:24,000
Your home?

357
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:26,120
Whose wife are you?

358
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:28,360
I loved you so much.

359
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:30,040
I waited two years for you.

360
00:14:30,760 --> 00:14:31,760
But now,

361
00:14:31,760 --> 00:14:34,120
you've teamed up with someone else to deceive me.

362
00:14:34,120 --> 00:14:34,880
Why?

363
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:36,760
Tell me why.

364
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:39,200
I'm the one who should be asking why.

365
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,520
Why did you kill Haohan?

366
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:43,440
Because I've been waiting eagerly,

367
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,600
coming for you.

368
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:54,520
You sent those flowers.

369
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,000
Yes.

370
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:59,000
He knew I was sending the flowers.

371
00:14:59,520 --> 00:15:01,980
He also knew I tampered with the insulation.

372
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:04,120
Yet he still dared to report me.

373
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:06,400
He really was a good man.

374
00:15:06,560 --> 00:15:08,090
Since he was such a good man,

375
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,460
if I hadn't killed him,

376
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:11,080
how could I be with you?

377
00:15:15,120 --> 00:15:16,760
There's something else you don't know.

378
00:15:16,760 --> 00:15:18,480
That night, when I saw

379
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:21,760
you were still crying over Yin Haohan,

380
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:26,200
I gave up completely.

381
00:15:26,920 --> 00:15:28,560
Do you know why I married you?

382
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:30,680
I just wanted revenge.

383
00:15:31,760 --> 00:15:33,620
You thought I actually loved you?

384
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:35,120
That's ridiculous.

385
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:37,560
I've told you everything you wanted to know.

386
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:38,820
Are you satisfied now?

387
00:15:42,680 --> 00:15:44,540
You didn't mishear a single word.

388
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:46,960
This is my revenge.

389
00:15:47,560 --> 00:15:48,600
I hate you.

390
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:51,140
I shouldn't have told you any of this.

391
00:15:51,280 --> 00:15:53,610
I should have kept you in the dark forever.

392
00:15:53,680 --> 00:15:54,320
That way,

393
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:56,480
your whole life would be a joke.

394
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:00,020
Are you satisfied?

395
00:16:00,480 --> 00:16:01,360
Are you happy?

396
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:02,920
Do you want to kill me?

397
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:04,520
Come on.

398
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:05,960
Do it.

399
00:16:11,760 --> 00:16:12,760
I hate you.

400
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,080
I hate you.

401
00:16:20,400 --> 00:16:21,280
I hate you.

402
00:17:04,280 --> 00:17:06,480
Why did you wipe the fingerprints off the massager

403
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:07,800
and put your own on it?

404
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:09,880
They're pitiful enough.

405
00:17:10,760 --> 00:17:12,079
Just punish me.

406
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:16,200
I watched He Huan slip away bit by bit.

407
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:17,160
I also saw

408
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:19,520
how Wang Luyang cried outside the ER.

409
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:21,599
I know how much pain he was in.

410
00:17:22,280 --> 00:17:25,000
I also know how hard Ning Yuxin's life has been this past year.

411
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:26,859
I'm not afraid of going to prison.

412
00:17:27,119 --> 00:17:28,560
Making me pay the price

413
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:30,080
will make me feel better.

414
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:35,580
It will also let me do right by Yin Haohan.

415
00:17:45,320 --> 00:17:47,600
Fate has played a cruel joke on me.

416
00:17:49,320 --> 00:17:52,120
Just when my life was at its happiest and sweetest,

417
00:17:53,960 --> 00:17:55,280
Yin Haohan died.

418
00:17:56,800 --> 00:17:59,200
Just when I decided to accept Cheng Jiancai

419
00:17:59,800 --> 00:18:02,460
and planned to spend the rest of my life with him,

420
00:18:03,120 --> 00:18:05,320
I learned that he killed my ex-husband.

421
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:06,960
Officers,

422
00:18:07,560 --> 00:18:09,420
don't you think it's ridiculous?

423
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:13,560
I hate Cheng Jiancai.

424
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:17,690
I hate that he stopped at nothing for his love.

425
00:18:17,800 --> 00:18:19,080
I hate his deception,

426
00:18:19,320 --> 00:18:20,480
his coldness,

427
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:23,280
and that he killed so many innocent people.

428
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:29,160
I used his money

429
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:33,130
to make it up to Ning Yuxin and Wang Luyang.

430
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:35,160
And used his death

431
00:18:37,120 --> 00:18:39,120
to atone for my guilt toward Haohan.

432
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:44,160
Do you regret it?

433
00:18:49,520 --> 00:18:49,720
...

434
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:51,800
Regret being blinded by hatred?

435
00:18:57,720 --> 00:18:58,520
No.

436
00:19:00,760 --> 00:19:02,080
I fell in love with him.
